{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0d2d95235e","title":"给鲁迅艺术学院文学团体“路社”的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"20f92a0d9e","index":0,"year":1939,"month":1,"day":21,"articleId":"0d2d95235e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dc99741b03","type":"paragraph","text":"给鲁迅艺术学院文学团体","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"0d2d95235e"},{"id":"f0e0f42b50","type":"paragraph","text":"“路社”的信","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"0d2d95235e"},{"id":"32575109ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年1月21日）路社常务委员会请同志信件收到了，谢谢你们的好意。二月四日已约定别的集会，不能来你处，请加原谅。问我关于诗歌的意见，我是外行，说不出成片段的意见来，只有一点，无论文艺的任何部门，包括诗歌在内，我觉都应是适合大众需要的才是好的。现在的东西中，有许多有一种毛病，不反映民众生活，因此也为民众所不懂。适合民众需要这种话是常谈，但此常谈很少能做到，我觉这是现在的缺点。这一点是否有考虑的价值，请你们期耐一番。此复。努力！敬祝","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"0d2d95235e"},{"id":"0bba3878ca","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东一月二十一日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"0d2d95235e"}],"page":{"id":"5cb0e892b8","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"0d2d95235e","start":183,"end":183}}}},"__N_SSG":true}